{"tid":588354,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（半遊記）即將去日本東京 第一日你講我去食","createTime":"2018-03-11T07:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T08:59:24.000Z","uid":133979,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f076bf3317f0d133471ef5c8e697a6a53e7e28","tid":588354,"uid":133979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:03:41.000Z","msg":"今日1550 將乘坐港航去日本NRT<br />\n屎忽痕又無plan 頭1 日行程<br />\n既然無咩野做都係尻行不如大家有咩想食又或者希望食到既 可以提出下<br />\n等我有d 目的咁尻行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食既野盡量滿足啦 <br />\n起碼唔好叫我食屎先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己就有個list <br />\n大致上都係拉面 例如無敵家 一燈果d 等等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/150122_05f631ce37189ee9cb64d5194341a52f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F150122_05f631ce37189ee9cb64d5194341a52f.png&h=5921dcc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等上飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be3170eb92324394565e431f6c1333e6b6683c6","tid":588354,"uid":175752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:13:03.000Z","msg":"無敵家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c15581039df865e07856c27701fe7148df3b847","tid":588354,"uid":85552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:15:14.000Z","msg":"數寄屋橋次郎"},{"pid":"5d2d7240886f691da3e7552326183f61c02b165e","tid":588354,"uid":54647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:28:41.000Z","msg":"天丼"},{"pid":"182daf1f35140cd0c4d401d5bdc2571918b4e1ea","tid":588354,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03